title: #214 - Bobby Lee & Khalyla
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast we welcome back Bobby & Khalyla of TigerBelly to the #27th podcast in the USA! Together we discuss the "pandy", relationships, role playing, Bobby's ear discharge, staying up all night playing video games, using your platform for good, and a whole lot more!
